high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the wall, then left to the diningtable with two chairs in front of it.
Pick up the eggplant from the table.
Turn around and go to the small coffeetable just ahead.
Place the eggplant down on the coffeetable.
Go back to the dresser you picked the eggplant up from, then turn right into the path with a drawer at the end.
Pick up the eggplant on the right of the drawer.
Return to the coffeetable you placed the first eggplant on.
Place the second eggplant down next to the first one on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Place two Eggplants on a CoffeeTable.

high_descs: Go left and head straight towards the wall. After that, turn left and walk straight into the room, turning to the dining table on your right.
Pick up egg plant from the dining table.
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the coffee table on your right.
Place egg plant on the coffee table.
Head straight towards the dresser by turning around and turning left.
Pick up egg plant from the dining table.
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the coffee table on your right.
Place egg plant on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Collecting egg plant from different places and arranging them on a  coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the dining table to your left
Pick up the eggplant from the dining table
Turn around and move to the coffee table
Place the eggplant on the coffee table
Turn right, walk straight and turn your right to reach the dresser
Pick up another eggplant from the dresser
Turn back and go to the coffee table to your left
Place the eggplant on the coffee table
anns.task_desc: Place the two eggplants on the coffee table
